snippet.title: Travellers Rest - Official City and Story Update Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2024
snippet.description: Travellers Rest is a farming life simulation game developed by Isolated Games. Players will use all the available tools to become the best tavern keeper in the realm. A new City and Story Update is arriving to the game soon bringing new content for players to enjoy. The City and Story Update for Travellers Rest is launching in July 2024 for PC (Steam).
